<blockquote><p align="right">     William Jennings Bryan</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></center><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ufoladen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>foladen</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Toede Fodder</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>153</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>12/19/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>10:54:23 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Suggestions</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Just a few suggestions to iron out the big brother idea (which will work great once we get it smoothed out.)<br>
<br>
1. guilds not calling in the big brother guild - be it pride or whatever this is unacceptable. We should establish that any guild that neglects to mention hey were leaving a god up when we are done lose their next posted raid. If we dont make it where people feel the need to call in bb, then many wont. It sounds extreme, but i see no other way to do it. Open to better ideas of course.<br>
<br>
2. Time deadline. lets say 10 pm PST. If a god is still up at that time. Contact should be established. If that guild is not going to take it down, then thats when the bb guild needs to be called in. This way this does not infringe on the next guild's planar date.<br>
<br>
3. Negotiations on loot - there are none. Epic item only unless hosting guild says you can have this. A member of the posting guild should be in each bb group so theres no debate about who loots what. too much conjecture there otherwise.<br>
<br>
4. Is there a way to see what bb guild is up on the rotation? if so , lets make it viewable from the main calendar screen. That way we have a viewable rotation.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uemilsinclair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Emil Sinclair</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Wog</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>9</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>12/19/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>11:11:15 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Suggestions</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Thanks Rewena,<br>
