(I don't get it either!)</font><P><CENTER><TABLE cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0 width=100%><TR><TD colspan=2><HR></TD></TR><TR valign=top><TD align=right><FONT Size=5><B><u>Chemistrius Ul'Veldrin   </u></B></FONT><BR><FONT size=-1>53<sup>rd</Sup> Season Dark Elf Rake<BR>Rogue in Exile</FONT></TD><TD><FONT size=-1>It will be a hard life.<BR>One without remorse, without reward, without regret.<BR>A path will be placed before you, the choice is yours alone.<BR>Do what you think you cannot do.<BR>It will be a hard life, but you will find out who you are.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD colspan=2><HR></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sylph>Sylph</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Wog</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>14</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>12/19/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>1:11:23 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Suggestions</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">The main issue here is the end time of the raid, after 2am the plane no longer belonged to PM, it belonged to RoS.<br>
